Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Federation's Third Fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...staged an attack on\Nthe space fortress, Solomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and broke into it using\Ntheir new weapon, the Solar System.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Zam's Last Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I botched it. I can't believe\NI could have been so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleggar's G-Fighter is returning to the ship.\NIt looks like the left engine has been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleggar! Do you copy?! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I read you.eck 3.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough missiles from starboard!\NDon't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, bring Chief Vammas\Nup from the sub-bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Private conversations are prohibited\Nduring battle... but don't shut me out, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think that I'm\Ncapable enough to watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'll always be here waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir?\N- Ensign Mirai isn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take over her position for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!\NI'll relieve you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-aircraft guns!\NObject approaching portside! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!\NDeal with the left engine when the fire's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Howard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta replace the busted armor panels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fuel pump to engine no. 2.\NI'm pretty sure there's a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And fill it up with fuel and ammo.\NMake it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got 10.\NI've gotta get re-fuelled myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!\NWe've got 10 minutes to fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Howard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Lieutenant Sleggar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was headed toward the waiting box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant! You're not injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign. What are you doing\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign. Enough of that.\NDon't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Sleggar. All prepared for takeoff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you later.\N- Lieutenant...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Mirai... When you're young,\Nthings can be very chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take your own feelings\Ntoo seriously at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...? Well... it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign, I'm not the kind of man\Nwho deserves your affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sleggar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You dazzle me, Ensign.\NWe're worlds apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a cheap ring...\Nbut it's a memento of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to lose it in space.\NHold onto it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after that ring, Ensign!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At Granada, Kycilia's base to the south\Nof the moon's Ural Mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...a fleet was preparing to take off\Nin an attempt to rescue Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The fleet had been swiftly assembled\Nunder the command of M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad... There are a lot of\Nenemy forces left inside the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! There's a new weapon! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! How many are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. It seems there's only one new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest are just Rick Doms and Zakus.\NLet's get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Hang on!\NWe don't know their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those measly pawns are coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them how the Big Zam differs from\Nany other mobile armor or mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna come out, come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My beams...!\NIt's a monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?\NI'll check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the control room!\NYour Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- What Is It?!, Your Excellency?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight in the Big Zam!\NSo many enemy mobile suits have entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But our remaining fleets\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- There's no need for you to fight In person!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached the point where\Nwe must use all our fighting strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mineva...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you've escaped to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an escape rocket. One of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Its course?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to have been launched\Nfrom Solomon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it in under remote control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the battle at Solomon\Nseems rather desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir?\N- Ignore the escape rocket and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon. But you don't\Nunderstand the feelings of soldiers in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't?\N- At times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers can fight in space,\Nrisking their own lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...because they believe their comrades\Nwill come to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, they'll drift out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mineva...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an allied fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased with this thing's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate,\Nour base will be badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Control room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes, Your Excellency. have left?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's new weapon and mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...have destroyed or immobilized\Nthree-quarters of our vessels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Tell the rest to charge\Nstraight through the enemy's main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll lead the remaining Rick Doms\Nand Zakus out of Solomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir! Good luck, Your Excellency!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, and the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we've confirmed\Nenemy fleet leaving Granada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- We can hold on a little longer, correct?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the remaining enemy vessels have\Nlaunched from the other side of Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get them with\Nwhat's left of the Solar System?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have a 60 percent chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Focal coordinates, 0-6-3-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Making minor adjustments to the Y-axis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,0-0-4! 0-0-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All fleets will finish off the enemy\Nafter we focus the Solar System!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the ships we passed.\NOthers are ahead! Hit whatever you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Next...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of machine\Ncould destroy mobile suits like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Another vessel leaving Solomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Receiving Solar System's\Ncoded focusing signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!\NThe Solar System's still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Remaining ships will charge\Nthe enemy's main force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the Big Zam's target?!\N- The command vessel that's in the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla's craft has been hit!\NWe'll take her in through Deck 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she's inside, we'll pursue the large\Nmobile armor that launched from Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble, Lieutenant.\NI'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Vammas,\Nplease return to the sub-bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the White Base around\N180 degrees, Mirai! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Salamis ships!\N- No problem! Fire forward beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!\NThat mobile armor isn't just big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw that thing deflect the beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means only missiles will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something,\Nwe'll just have more casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Zam will charge the main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But first give a flare to signal\Nthat all units are to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our forces have been battered too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to abandon Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch control over to my panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you men must escape as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- But... Your Excellency?!\N- Don't waste your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Doms and Zakus.\NThey can pull you off the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Send out the flare signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking over the Big Zam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected Solomon\Nto fall so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't fire on unarmed men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Big Zam!\NThose long-range beams have no effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take as many of you as I can\Nwith me to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The large mobile suit is emitting\Na powerful magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles! Intercept with missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Big Zam is mass-produced\Nwe'll put an end to the Federation in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Sleggar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to dock...\Nand charge into them in G-Armor mode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Let's do It, Chief Amuro!hat's your plan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't talk to me about plans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their magnetic field, all we can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If these beam cannons fall...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...use the Gundam's beam rifle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With three levels of weaponry on our side,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Sleggar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget personal feelings.\NI won't let it create any more casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds sad. But this is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! We'll attack from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,From below?! Anti-air defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not over yet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a single mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...going to defeat the Big Zam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won't be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let a punk like you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For the glory of Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For my own pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not defeat me!\NYou will not defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Solomon has fallen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this? Captain, you'll take Lady Zenna\Nto Granada aboard this Gwazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll board a Chivvay so that I can\Nkeep an eye on the Federation's next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We've missed our chance\Nto stage a surprise attack, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your role as strategist depended on\NSolomon holding out until we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave a few vessels to collect intelligence\Nand rescue the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll help with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell me it's a lie, can you, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,tsubasa wo hirogete anata wo matsuwa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll spread my wings and wait for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,kyou no anata wa tsuraino kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you're suffering today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sonna koto nai watashitachi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not feel such things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,dakara ne oyasumi Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So please sleep now, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,konna jidai to hito wa iu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,People say our times are awful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,kono nukumori ga tashika nara tashika nara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If this warmth is real for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,mitsukaruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:23:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,yume sore wa yume yume
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:23:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream, it is a dream, a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Char prepares himself for the next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unaware, Amuro and M'Quve fight a\Nmortal combat in an uninhabited wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As she observes the battle, young Lalah\Nhas visions of her destiny calling for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NThe Duel in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode\NThe Duel in Texas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duel in Texas
